data.meta_description: EVANGELINE MYERS WEDS V. BARNETT IN FLORIDA -- On Sunday, August 12 [1945], at 12:30 o'clock, noon, the Little Temple Methodist Church of Miami, Fla., was the scene of a very simple wedding ceremony. Miss Evangeline Myers, daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Homer E. Myers, Sligo, Pa., was united in marriage to Vance Barnett,...
